Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向往天空 亲近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔于天空的神秘力量开始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天之边际云之彼方存在着一片黄金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事讲述了一个追寻梦想自由生存的天空盗贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空盗团少年——酷的波澜起伏的爱和冒险的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵达守护翼的酷一行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上层人物的干预下被迫与蕾分开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.89,0:02:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并被告知不可能再见到蕾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.72,0:02:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 沉浸在煌珠乐园的幻影中的蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在自称伊芙的神密人物的指引下回到了现实世界中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.63,0:02:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混乱之中 决定独自一人前往煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.85,0:02:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时 知道了这一情况的酷离开了守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.78,0:02:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年和少女能再次相遇吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.71,0:02:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借防御属性探测煌珠的所在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.08,0:02:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对绝对能帮上你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.61,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.65,0:03:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作需要你的这种能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.14,0:03:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十四唱 煌珠猎人、再度来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾 不是说好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.78,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我带你去煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你居然一个人走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾 我一定会去找你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.07,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库鲁斯辅佐官 请解释一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜的战斗究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷被人袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 守护翼总部居然受到攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细情况现在正在调查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再具体的就不能告诉你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.67,0:04:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方真的是叫做ChaosChoir的组织吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也在调查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我再问一个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.76,0:04:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要分开酷和蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉撒蒂和莉莉雅两人生活在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是酷和蕾却没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.53,0:04:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾也不在城里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.50,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白身为七煌宝树的蕾是个特殊的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但做到这份上就太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他们说好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带他们去煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.46,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不但违背了和他们的约定还把他们强制隔离开来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和欺骗他们没什么区别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的是保护煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道所做的一切不是为了保护她们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的举措也是以此为理念而采取的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.41,0:05:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是守护翼民意决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 蕾现在在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也正在调查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就把这个任务交给我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.34,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 搜索任务已经交由别人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指定的猎物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.31,0:06:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.69,0:06:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.54,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方法随你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快回收她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.03,0:06:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 守护翼不也和我们猎人一样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.58,0:06:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁 工作的事情谈完了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.67,0:06:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.38,0:06:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会非常非常努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.37,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和卧鲁合作的话不管什么工作都能轻松搞定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只不过是道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话任我使唤就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.11,0:07:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道乘火车到了这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾 你到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.01,0:07:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.24,0:07:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你已不在这城市了吗 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.85,0:07:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就老老实实地回来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.06,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩真是没用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你那么说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各自房里待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是库鲁斯辅佐官的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管方式如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.62,0:08:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护翼保护煌珠这一理念是没有错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.66,0:08:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他库鲁斯啊守护翼啊这样那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话那些根本不用加以理睬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希丝卡 你想怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷可是毫不犹豫地冲出去了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.76,0:08:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.80,0:08:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见他们俩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.98,0:08:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到了想跟他们道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.65,0:08:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想去就不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么简单的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和前辈的心情一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.87,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有库鲁斯辅佐官的命令在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.58,0:09:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休假申请啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.02,0:09:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接到下一个命令之前拿到休假就没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得你这么聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.50,0:09:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我教导有方的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.16,0:09:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总觉得有点太容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 看看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我的装备样式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 库鲁斯辅佐官他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.14,0:09:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那位大人比谁都更理解我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是爱的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.63,0:09:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库鲁斯辅佐官 希丝卡 希丝卡我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙 快点走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.89,0:10:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有制服有时会更方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 小气鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我坐一下又有什么关系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世道艰辛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都无视我走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得快点追上蕾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 这次一定要成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.02,0:10:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 载我去邻村好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.19,0:10:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指蕾吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要找蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.86,0:10:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是煌珠猎人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯上猎物是理所应当的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧的是 蕾她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.99,0:11:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧的是 我不会把蕾轻易交给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你同契了的话就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先把你解决了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.83,0:11:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁 附近没有煌珠的迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是先问出她的下落为好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别对我指手画脚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然来这一套啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎物就要全力追捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你还是快点同契为好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西是七煌宝树吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你连这个也知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.55,0:11:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不同寻常的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.95,0:11:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为和那东西同契了 你才能活到现在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别张口闭口“那东西”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾可不是物体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西就是物体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为战斗而存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是武器而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听见我说不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种对手我一个人就足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.13,0:12:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 绝对不能把蕾交给那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.63,0:12:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福音响起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小命我拿下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁 果然很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近没有煌珠的迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器竟敢对我指手画脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替代你的道具是要多少有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.86,0:13:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归根到底还不是把那女孩当武器或道具来用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.48,0:13:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然的确和蕾多次同契一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.66,0:13:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.33,0:13:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使没有战斗我也想待在蕾的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让蕾陪在我的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道没有这样的想法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道具终究只是道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在使用这东西而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.37,0:13:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些煌珠们就是为了被我们使用才存在着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无其它活下去的办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.06,0:13:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有踪影啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.13,0:14:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多应该追上酷了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那边 看那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.71,0:14:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆摩托车...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我交给酷的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.54,0:14:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该就在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们兵分两路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是逃不掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许应该想个办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那家伙不跟我交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有七煌宝树这样的武器却为何...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁 冷静啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有什么阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让我一再重复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.49,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想过那样的日子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.35,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说过了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.64,0:15:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用那女孩这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是只凭自己的力量就战斗不了的家伙的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要靠我自己的实力打败你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁 小心上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 已经结束了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希丝卡 你怎么会在这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话应该我说才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你离开守护翼去追赶蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.19,0:16:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然在这种地方和煌珠猎人打斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他追着我不放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手脚笨拙也是一个原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真干得了空贼这一行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.72,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追究起来难道不是你们把我和蕾分开才惹出来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个的确如你所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.09,0:16:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好能让你们在一起的却弄成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借口就不找了 真的是太对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 希丝卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这和那是两回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.89,0:16:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们提前半天跑出来为什么还在这里瞎转悠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又迷路了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.23,0:16:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是想要干什么 道歉还是教训我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好竖起耳朵听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是一次又一次...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.02,0:16:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的作战方案啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.74,0:17:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.23,0:17:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你们还真是有缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 应该机缘巧合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉露露 同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再跟我同契一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.15,0:17:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经没有同契的力气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能战斗的话就没你什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去找个代替品罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.33,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.19,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类 人类就那么了不起吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.02,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有资格把保护你的煌珠叫做物体吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把物体叫做物体有什么不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用的道具只会生锈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.12,0:18:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用到坏掉为止才是这些家伙们的夙愿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是人类自私的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.57,0:18:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们守护翼又如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.44,0:18:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管以什么为借口 所作所为不也和我没多大区别吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.09,0:18:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保护的名义下隔离煌珠 剥夺她们的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.72,0:18:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的你们没有资格来否定我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.67,0:18:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.51,0:18:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为有你这样的人存在我们才必须保护煌珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们并不是什么武器或物体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.77,0:18:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了创造能和守护者共存的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.70,0:18:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以守护翼的名义与你战斗到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎么狡辩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.32,0:18:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠是道具这一事实是不会改变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.90,0:18:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在你能安然无恙却又是为何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌珠是给人使用的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就在此把你打倒为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁由我来保护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.83,0:19:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们碰他一根手指的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.44,0:19:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉露露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是道具或武器都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.97,0:19:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为卧鲁...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.16,0:19:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁说了需要我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.13,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要保护卧鲁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对绝对要保护你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.12,0:19:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.48,0:19:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是那孩子赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.91,0:20:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧鲁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 没想到你们都会追上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就是违抗了命令吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式请假过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是带薪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.53,0:20:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 虽说是休假但也没丢下守护翼的理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.19,0:20:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护翼就是守护煌珠的双翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.12,0:20:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个理念铭刻在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.09,0:20:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.92,0:20:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.99,0:20:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家一起再次向蕾的所在出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么酷会坐在驾驶座上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.95,0:20:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.76,0:21:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也阻止不了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.40,0:22:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之谷中风止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.31,0:22:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已成了悲伤之谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.74,0:22:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空的少年啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.87,0:22:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次让风吹起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.03,0:23:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 大风车之村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.19,0:23:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五唱 大风车之村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.15,0:23:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心灵深处 少女一直在等待着
